{"tid":1192280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［真人真事］ 頭先我係 ig story 呼籲班朋友一齊遊行","createTime":"2019-06-08T10:42:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T10:51:23.000Z","uid":113946,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fd9b4a9aa8bb655476f6a6dd6f232b9252f08527","tid":1192280,"uid":113946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T10:42:17.000Z","msg":"我當時就咁打咗句「希望可以係銅鑼灣見到大家，六月九號見」<br />\n跟住就收到個前同事whatsapp<br />\n而我個前同事係新移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：前同事<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：聽日去遊行啊？你係點報名去遊行架？！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：吓 遊行係直接係集合地點等 唔洗報名架！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：真定假啊？！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我係 whatsapp 見到有招募人去銅鑼灣遊行 1000蚊一日 我尋晚打電話去聯絡佢但打唔通 到今日佢已經話夠人唔請人啦<br />\n<br />\n當時我開始嬲 覺得咁樣收錢遊行同賣港無分別 但我見佢係新移民 希望可以令佢明白究竟呢個反送中遊行背後有咩意義<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你報名參加係支持送中條例 但我參加係反對啊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：吓 但我支持架 我覺得呢個條例對香港係好嘅<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你反對個邊仲要唔要人啊 要的話我去啊 你幫我問下啊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我地遊行係自願 我更唔會為錢而出賣自己良心<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：呢次反送中一但失敗 香港就等如變成中國一部分架啦<br />\n<br />\n我無諗過身邊真係會有人咁樣為錢賣港 認真講我係有少少心淡 但係係危急存亡之秋我地更加要出黎唔可以認輸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我相信我地可以成功"},{"pid":"6a7b78c71696199ae4caca7b6e3639184f811ebc","tid":1192280,"uid":41389,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T10:42:42.000Z","msg":"-遊行起點：銅鑼灣維多利亞公園中央草坪 （維園草地）<br />\n-遊行路線：維園草地起點&gt;高士威道&gt; 禮頓道&gt;伊榮街&gt;邊寧頓街&gt;軒尼詩道西行車路&gt;金鐘道&gt;樂禮街&gt;夏愨道&gt;添美道&gt;立法會外行人路終點<br />\n-集合時間：2：30PM<br />\n-起步時間：3：00PM（或維園草地達八成滿）<br />\n-衝定唔衝，自己執生<br />\n-記得宗旨：不散<br />\n<br />\n溫和：<br />\n<strong>【長期置頂】69反送中遊行須知整合</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1191837/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1191837/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[懶人包] 第一次參加遊行的常見疑問Q&amp;A</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1186623/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1186623/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【極重要】69遊行記得帶防Rfid卡套</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1190797/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1190797/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n勇武： <br />\n<strong>食放題須知，全部資料，一世受用</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1191403/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1191403/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[law撚］被捕人仕須知</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1189300/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1189300/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>［抗爭手冊］End game前準備</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1169374/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1169374/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑色三毛警告信號現正生效 6月8日16時</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">表示連登 facebook 網絡廣泛地區已錄得或預料會有每秒三毛回覆量超過70次/禁70次正評的網絡分化攻勢，且攻勢可能持續或於今晚或明朝早上升級。</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNv7C24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNv7C24.jpg&h=73f7da13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">注意事項</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong>網民應注意username 同 三毛開post 目的 而非三毛post正評數量。<br />\n網民應負皮三毛post 入去屌佢老母 而毋須參與分化討論。<br />\n鍵盤戰士應努力推正經post 例如準備時項去抵擋三毛攻勢。<br />\n三毛會開一啲反共post 減低大家戒心 請細心思考現時網絡上所有言論。<br />\n一般市民應少上連登 關電視 而休養等待明天遊行。<br />\n鬼得一隻 林奠 其他完全唔重要 。</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZB4gyv7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZB4gyv7.gif&h=7cacc0df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4626660c3ee83049181d64944c5b5383b476ee0","tid":1192280,"uid":76591,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T10:43:15.000Z","msg":"支持就咪移民落香港，叫佢死翻上大灣區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0740463a066153d4f4a034c04ad7b463d30e4aa9","tid":1192280,"uid":160605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T10:44:00.000Z","msg":"同某TUBER一鳩樣，為左錢賣港<br />\n大陸有生意比佢，叫佢唔好出聲，咁唔出囉<br />\n真心笑死我"},{"pid":"6eeee7affc309cce36d93676fb5067658269f9c3","tid":1192280,"uid":148817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T10:44:04.000Z","msg":"screen cap please"},{"pid":"b9457b8a8d6ba0aacc72bc9665c40e9290bfeacd","tid":1192280,"uid":113946,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"6eeee7affc309cce36d93676fb5067658269f9c3","tid":1192280,"uid":148817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T10:44:04.000Z","msg":"screen cap please"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T10:48:55.000Z","msg":"我地對話全部都係錄音 cap 咗上黎都無用 更何況我都無必要講大話啦"},{"pid":"ab1b1bb5e9f37a2bbe816868c0188ffdb3bbc166","tid":1192280,"uid":180949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T10:49:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記得有幾多人叫幾多人出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"ea1040ea4a516654fe94876d4733eb38706db89d","tid":1192280,"uid":113946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T10:51:23.000Z","msg":"Between 依家啲新移民都係合適翻去中國生活 唔好落黎拖累香港啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}